            <div type="translation">
                <p>of ...nach son of ?</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The fragmentary first name is an adjectival formation with the suffix *‑āko- (OIr. -ach), either built on an n-stem noun, or on a thematic base with a stem in -n.</p>
